  "title": "2022 AMC 10A Problems/Problem 1",
  "problem": "What is the value of \\[3+\\frac{1}{3+\\frac{1}{3+\\frac13}}?\\] $\\textbf{(A)}\\ \\frac{31}{10}\\qquad\\textbf{(B)}\\ \\frac{49}{15}\\qquad\\textbf{(C)}\\ \\frac{33}{10}\\qquad\\textbf{(D)}\\ \\frac{109}{33}\\qquad\\textbf{(E)}\\ \\frac{15}{4}$",
  "solution": "We have \\begin{align*} 3+\\frac{1}{3+\\frac{1}{3+\\frac13}} &= 3+\\frac{1}{3+\\frac{1}{\\left(\\frac{10}{3}\\right)}} \\\\ &= 3+\\frac{1}{3+\\frac{3}{10}} \\\\ &= 3+\\frac{1}{\\left(\\frac{33}{10}\\right)} \\\\ &= 3+\\frac{10}{33} \\\\ &= \\boxed{\\textbf{(D)}\\ \\frac{109}{33}}. \\end{align*} ~MRENTHUSIASM",
